Welcome to Kuma.

To run developer-local.allizom.org, run:
    foreman start

    (Consult ~/src/Procfile to see what services are managed by Foreman.)

To run Kuma tests:
    make test

To run KumaScript tests:
    cd ~/src/kumascript && ./node_modules/.bin/nodeunit tests

To clean built assets and remove pyc files:

    make clean

To compile and collect static files:

    make compilecss compilejsi18n collectstatic

To update this dev environment run from the host machine:
    vagrant provision
